<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Security Alert - {{app_name}}</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h2>Security Alert</h2>
    <p>Hello {{data.full_name}},</p>
    <p>We detected a security event related to your {{app_name}} account.</p>
    
    <div style="background-color: #fff3cd; padding: 20px; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid #ffeeba;">
        <h3>Alert Details</h3>
        <p><strong>Type:</strong> {{data.alert_type}}</p>
        <p><strong>Time:</strong> {{data.timestamp}}</p>
        <p><strong>Details:</strong> {{data.details}}</p>
    </div>
    
    <p>If you recognize this activity, no action is needed. If you did not perform this action, please:</p>
    <ol>
        <li>Change your password immediately</li>
        <li>Enable two-factor authentication if not already enabled</li>
        <li>Contact our support team</li>
    </ol>
    
    <p><a href="{{app_url}}/security" style="background-color: #dc3545; color: white; padding: 14px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px;">Review Account Security</a></p>
    
    <p>Best regards,<br>
    The {{app_name}} Security Team</p>
    
    <hr>
    <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #666;">
        For immediate assistance, please contact us at {{support_email}}
    </p>
</body>
</html>
